name: Troll
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Troll is just a meme coin that is run by the community.

What makes your project unique?
It is not unique, it is like any other memecoin, we just TROLL + We have a renounced contract.

History of your project.
Was created by a group of degens 2 weeks ago and have slowly worked in building a community.

What’s next for your project?
Currently we are working on developing an APP which will bring more memes to the space.

What can your token be used for?
It is a community token for the moment, which is totally run by them.
